This module manages rbldnsd on Debian.

This was forked from Matt Taggart <taggart@riseup.net>
https://labs.riseup.net/code/projects/module-rbldnsd/

Changes by Rudy Gevaert
https://github.com/rgevaert/puppet-rbldnsd

- Split up the init.pp to use other pattern
- Make puppet-lint happy
- Supports Puppet 4
- Rspec and acceptance tests
